title: Tom Hiddleston wants you to eat cake. Immediately

json.text: Love eating cake, I don't have a problem with eating cake. The thing is I think eating cake
is a genuine pleasure and so I don't feel guilty about it.
Very happy to eat as much cake as I choose and I think people should eat more cake,
if they want, don't if you don't.
Yeah, I try not feel guilty about pleasures. I think if it's a pleasure that's not hurting
anyone else, I think you should indulge it and not feel guilty about it.
